sect1.title: General
sect1.para: Purpose of ZenturHSM: ZenturHSM contains two components: the 3rd party ZenturHSM and the ZenturHSM Integration CDD The ZenturHSM integration component uses the ZenturHSM.c file and the corresponding header file in order to provide the startup routine for HSM and mechanism to write SHE slots via UDS
